text: Yalla kinni Qaranwaa kee baaxóoy ken addal tanim lica ayróh addat gintem, wohuk naharat kay Qarshi leê bagul suge, Yalli taamâ maqaaneh siinik yayse mara yaaxaguh sin mokkora, Nabiyow atu ama korosuk diggah isin rabteeniik gamadal nuwwuk ugsan mara akketton keeenik ittek, diggah koroosite mari ama Qhuraanay atu nel takriye tu hinna baxxaqqa iyya baab akke waytek kok axcelon
